gmoji\" /> 都唔同類型 唔好成日吹奏啦</blockquote><br />\n睇過一次就唔會覺得係吹奏<br />\n<br />\n套戲當年少人睇冇獎<br />\n最後出租影碟口卑超好<br />\nNetflix個D仍然好多人睇同讚<br />\n廿幾年後imdb仍然係9.3/10<br />\n連戲中演員依家都仲有分紅賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91abed98dd6949f90fee31e213f2dd109476e956","tid":341453,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T19:39:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/31/033909_6a8fdfc5c710243d78e30c6a8b2583e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F31%2F033909_6a8fdfc5c710243d78e30c6a8b2583e0.jpg&h=6fb20fd9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"70b9fe766b25f5e1269223b90e00564087226f60","tid":341453,"uid":31859,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T19:45:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇完比Titanic早幾年拍嘅月黑高飛<br />\n你就知乜野係神級<br />\n唔駛特技<br />\n剩係靠幾個好演員就好好睇<br />\n<br />\nTitanic係比D少女搵個白馬王子睇</blockquote><br />\n屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都唔同類型 唔好成日吹奏啦</blockquote><br />\n睇過一次就唔會覺得係吹奏<br />\n<br />\n套戲當年少人睇冇獎<br />\n最後出租影碟口卑超好<br />\nNetflix個D仍然好多人睇同讚<br />\n廿幾年後imdb仍然係9.3/10<br />\n連戲中演員依家都仲有分紅賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇過好多次啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該你睇多啲戲先啦 我都覺係神作好好睇 不過有必要入個唔關事嘅post踩套戲抬高自己鍾意啲戲咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10650e74e35fef66f5ca0d128889a50899f525c5","tid":341453,"uid":27616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T20:03:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/31/033236_08b1b467d67b58fd7e9519bae8d61f43.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F31%2F033236_08b1b467d67b58fd7e9519bae8d61f43.jpg&h=8abd5dfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n月黑高飛先認真係神片<br />\