like":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T04:15:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今年至少Logan、La La Land、Gifted都劇情好感人<br />\n你唔比錢入場睇就以為近年少戲正<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTitanic我學生哥時都入場睇啦<br />\n當年不知幾多少女入場翻睇幾次以上<br />\n大特技CG片係電視睇好浪費<br />\n你2017年先睇仲好似發現新大陸咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n勸你得閒入場睇多D戲增闊下眼界<br />\n係大戲院睇同係電視睇感覺差好遠</blockquote><br />\n我都會比錢入場睇 問題係有冇興趣姐 唔通每月出新電影我都要去睇咩 同埋冇時間係最大既問題 <br />\n同埋我都想當年睇呀 邊唔知係戲院睇個feel係好好多 不過當年得2歲想我點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10505e61856d8ad5ecb3a38cbececdaeae4162df","tid":341453,"uid":29719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T04:24:42.000Z","msg":"最尾個幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8a2116a31e4b138294a2da9bca891b04400c1f5","tid":341453,"uid":4635,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T05:02:08.000Z","msg":"細個會成日翻睇畫畫果幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae3c9862c6c69c274589d6f9ced045a5345082d","tid":341453,"uid":18385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T06:57:39.000Z","msg":"But this ship can't sink"}]}